Lines.Comment: Spoken as if he's talking to a waiter.
I can offer you unlimited power.
Now let's give these guys a hell of a show!
Hey, things are looking up already!
Yeah, yeah, sure, I'll see ya AROUND... You get it? Cuz you're gonna explode? Oh man, I kill myself.
This is gonna be a blast.
If it were up to me, you'd be on the other side of this battle.
Allies like you make me want to stand alone.
Are you kidding me? I WILL bash you in the face you know.
Stay behind me, and blow up anything that gets in our way!
Are you willing to put aside your differences with the Alliance, and partner with a draenei?
